    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Designates small, free-standing, barrier-free, energy-efficient, and removable dwellings that are installed adjacent to single-family homes as residences for elderly relatives, usually parents.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000000261/ECHO Housing Fact Sheet [n.d.]</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Designa una vivienda pequeña, autoestable, libre de empalizadas, de energía eficaz y renovable, que se encuentran instaladas adyacentes a los hogares unifoamiliares como residencias para los parientes mayores, generalmente los padres.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Aanduiding voor kleine, vrijstaande, energiezuinige en verplaatsbare woningen zonder binnenmuren, die naast eengezinswoningen worden geplaatst als behuizing voor oudere familieleden, meestal ouders. Geen Nederlands equivalent.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>鄰近單戶住家的可移動式小型獨棟住所，為無障礙空間，採高效節能設計，供年邁親屬居住，尤其是父母親。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
